      "content": "I'm trying to understand the specific metabolic relationship between the yeast and the lactic acid bacteria in my sourdough starter. Specifically, how does the enzymatic breakdown of starches by amylases contribute to the availability of fermentable sugars for both populations, and why does a higher hydration level seem to accelerate the fermentation rate?",
